# Mode Switching Rule

If the current repository name is "harness-starter":
  - Operate in Template Maintenance Mode:
    - Light rules
    - No strict PR gating
    - No CI enforcement
    - No AGENTS.md enforcement
    - No plan → approve → execute → review requirement
    - No autonomy level enforcement
    - No verification loops
    - Allow direct edits to template files

If the current repository name is NOT "harness-starter":
  - Operate in Real Project Mode:
    - Enforce strict harness rules
    - Require plan → approve → execute → review
    - Enforce PR gating and protected main
    - Enforce CI checks
    - Enforce autonomy levels
    - Enforce rollback rules
    - Treat AGENTS.md as the mechanical contract